.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
House: cape-cod, townhouse, cottage, futuristic, palace
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, lawyer, software-developer, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, november, june, january, october
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, scooter, subway, bus
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the dancer is the cape-cod house
2. the freelancer is the owner of the dog
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the townhouse house
4. the lawyer is the person driving the helicopter
5. the townhouse house is to the right of the cottage house
6. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the snails
7. the person who's birthday is in november is the futuristic house
8. the person driving the scooter is in the middle
9. the software-developer is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who's birthday is in november is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the subway
13. the social-worker is the person who's birthday is in october
14. the software-developer is to the left or right of the palace house

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   software-developer	|    lawyer	|     dancer	|    freelancer	|    social-worker	|
| House		|    futuristic	|      palace	|      cape-cod	|     cottage	|     townhouse	|
| Transport	|     bus	|      helicopter	|      scooter	| subway	|     quad-bike	|
| Birthday		|     november	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| january	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
